TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: User Defined Join
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_SRC_CD = VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_CNTL.EXTNL_SRC_CD and VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.EXTL_LVL1_ID = VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_CNTL.EXTL_LVL1_ID AND VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_STG.CLM_GID=VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.CLM_GID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Source Filter
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.INV_ELIG_DT>=DATE($$MAX_QTR_STRT_DT) AND VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.INV_ELIG_DT<=DATE($$MAX_QTR_END_DT) AND VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV.NRE_CLM_CD ='0' AND VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_CNTL.CSTM_DATA_CD= 1 AND VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_CNTL.DATA_PULL_EFF_DT <= DATE($$MAX_QTR_END_DT) AND VRAP.TCSTM_DATA_CNTL.DATA_PULL_TERM_DT >= DATE($$MAX_QTR_STRT_DT )
